title: Ep. - 421 - REAL HOUSEWIVES OF MIAMI REVIEW THE MURDERS AT STARVED ROCK
description:
Kate reviews The Murders at Starved Rock on HBO Max, a three-part docuseries directed by Jody McVeigh-Schultz looks back at the murders and the effect that they had on the Illinois River Valley region, the families of the women, and on Chester Weger, who spent 60 years in prison for the murders until he was released on parole last year. 

 

Brian Moylan and Kate review the premiere of Real Housewives of Miami on Peacock.
